=Description=

"The Luddites200 Organising Forum is an ad hoc group of admirers of the Luddites, radical historians and activists on issues connected to technology. We are scientists, musicians, poets, environmental and social justice campaigners.

As our name says, we aim to be a forum for anyone interested in this anniversary and what it means today. We want to encourage as many initiatives as possible around the country - just let us know what you're doing!"
(http://www.luddites200.org.uk/aboutus.htm)


